snippet.title: Dicejunkies Ep 171 Pt 2:  Johnny Depp Wins Lawsuit Vs Amber Heard!
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Dicejunkies Podcast Ep. 171 part 2. This week is with our crew, Xenodamus and Q. This week we discuss the Johnny Depp's lawsuit win Vs Amber Heard in ACLU donation investigation and more. We also have some random encounters, some sideline comments, and more as we look at the passed week in geek culture and roll some random encounters. If you want to join in the conversation we try to record each week on Sunday at 3:30 on Twitch. Every week this is were we talk about games, movies, tabletop, comics and an assortment of other geek culture topics. Be sure to Visit our website at dicejunkies.com, to keep up to date on everything we do. Be sure to bookmark and check it out as we continue to increase the content and entertainment options for you and all our Dicejunkies community. Dicejunkies is active on YouTube, Facebook, Twitter, Twitch, and Instagram. You can become a supporter of Dicejunkies on our Patreon page. Thanks for listening and be sure to check us out on Facebook, YouTube and our website, www.dicejunkies.com, where you can like, subscribe, and leave a comment.

Thanks for checking out this video.  Let us know what you think in the comments and be sure to like, subscribe, and hit that notification bell.
